    "description": "为了实现爷爷的梦想，探寻想象中天堂岛的Pino遭到了身份不明的生物的袭击，被迫坠落到了天堂岛。 Pino在探索各个岛屿时被卷入了世界中。请帮助Pino修复坏掉的飞机，击败怪物，并安全地回家！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/e2e4ac8af82a33642c7bcc1028fee530.poster.avif?t=1680489113\" width=798 height=446 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/e2e4ac8af82a33642c7bcc1028fee530.webm?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/e2e4ac8af82a33642c7bcc1028fee530.mp4?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>游戏<strong>'天堂岛'</strong>是由韩国大学生聚集制作的<strong>四视图休闲冒险游戏</strong>。玩家使用剑，长枪，铁锤作为主要武器，并使用弓作为辅助武器，击败攻击自己的怪物。每种武器都有一种技能，可以通过强化技能来对抗更强大的敌人。<br><br><strong>诱人背景</strong><br>游戏的背景以4个岛屿为主题<br>蓝天和清新的草地和花朵盛开的春岛“Epirus”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/20b7882edb0542187f18a36d4e57fbae.poster.avif?t=1680489113\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/20b7882edb0542187f18a36d4e57fbae.webm?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/20b7882edb0542187f18a36d4e57fbae.mp4?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有森林和巨大的树木，镇子的夏岛“Io”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/d7ad9398808e4733e17f8c4564c99d9e.poster.avif?t=1680489113\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/d7ad9398808e4733e17f8c4564c99d9e.webm?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/d7ad9398808e4733e17f8c4564c99d9e.mp4?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>随时不知何时会冒出怪物的田地和蘑菇盛开的秋岛“Thessaly”<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/4f0b1f89ad866bce81002de2d63fb738.poster.avif?t=1680489113\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/4f0b1f89ad866bce81002de2d63fb738.webm?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/4f0b1f89ad866bce81002de2d63fb738.mp4?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>所有东西都冻结，只有巨石生活的冬岛“Crete”。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/2492fac32d6ff3c2843deb31d09d1503.poster.avif?t=1680489113\" width=800 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/2492fac32d6ff3c2843deb31d09d1503.webm?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2302640/extras/2492fac32d6ff3c2843deb31d09d1503.mp4?t=1680489113\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>请享受美妙的故事和精美的背景图形！<br><br><br><br>-----------------------------------------------------------------<br>Sound support - Artive Sound <a href=\"mailto:Team(official@artivesound.com)\">Team(official@artivesound.com)</a><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >帮助翻译</h2>日文：정재현<br>法语：费利克斯-拉法格<br>西班牙文 : Sergi Castarnado Ordóñez",
